msgctxt "Comment"
msgid "Process finished in a non-focused monitored session"
msgstr "अकेन्द्रितनिरीक्षितसत्रे प्रक्रिया समाप्तवती"

#: desktop/konsole.notifyrc:945
msgctxt "Name"
